# ── PRIVACY MODE ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your tracker, contacts, and application packs contain your
# personal job hunt. If your fork is PUBLIC, uncomment these
# lines to keep working data out of git (the templates ship
# with an underscore prefix, so they stay tracked):
#
# pipeline/tracker.csv
# pipeline/target-companies.md
# pipeline/clusters/*
# !pipeline/clusters/_TEMPLATE.md
# pipeline/packs/*
# !pipeline/packs/_TEMPLATE.md
# pipeline/projects/*
# !pipeline/projects/_SPEC_TEMPLATE.md
# PLAN.md
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
